name: behavioral impulse
description: this was made for objkt4objkt #4 using frames generated over the last few weeks . as is often the case, i wasn't yet sure what to do with them, until today... this is a composite of robert oppenheimer, and a shot of the castle bravo 14.8 megaton nuclear test in 1954, glitched and processed to video . i have a fascination with historical moments such as these, they serve as stark reminder of the chaos we are capable of inflicting upon ourselves | Brendan Forde | @acid_very
